<p>英 /ə'dʒʌstmənt/    美 /ə'dʒʌstmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>调整；调节；适应：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I tried to <strong>make</strong> the necessary <strong>adjustment</strong> to this new situation<strong>to_2</strong>
我努力适应这里的新环境。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Some schools will have to make <strong><em>_</em></strong> in agreement with the national soccer reform.  （2015 江苏）<br />
